<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>URL Shortener</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8ffae 0%, #43c6ac 100%);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            color: #333;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        form {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        input[type="url"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border: 2px solid #43c6ac;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: border-color 0.3s;
        }

        input[type="url"]:focus {
            border-color: #f8ffae;
            outline: none;
        }

        button {
            background: #43c6ac;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.2s;
        }

        button:hover {
            background: #f8ffae;
            color: #333;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        section:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to Our URL Shortener</h1>
        <p>Shorten your long URLs quickly and easily!</p>
        <form action="/shorten" method="POST">
            <input type="url" name="url" placeholder="Enter URL" required>
            <button type="submit">Shorten</button>
        </form>
    </div>

    <section id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>CONNECT WITH ME</h2>
            <p>We are a simple and efficient URL shortening service. Try us out!</p>
            <a href="https://github.com/CHIRANJEET12"><button >Contact Us</button></a>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/chiranjeet-dwivedy-17a143279/"><button>LINKEDIN</button></a>
        </div>
    </section>




</body>
</html>
